observation.description:
EVSC380

- Flat-topped flower bunches.
- Flowers not all ligulate, both types of flowers
- narrow pinnate leaves.
- Late season/ dry weather has resulted in this specimen being colorless and dry.

Common Plants of the Western Rangelands Volume 3: Forbs, Kathy Tannas 2004
